_sText:
Fy_Munitions

A lot of cash has been found in a abandoned munitions bunker.
Terrorists wants to steal it and Counterterrorists needs to secure it.


Made By MNTL
Kasper Madsen

--------------
32 Spawnpoints
Recommended Players 12-16

Weapons are placed around the map on ammo crates.
There is only 1 of each weapon and 4 HE grenades.
